commentText: If set this option to be true, camel-ftp will use the list file directly to check if the file exists._Since some FTP server may not support to list the file directly, if the option is false,_camel-ftp will use the old way to list the directory and check if the file exists._This option also influences readLock=changed to control whether it performs a fast check to update file information or not._This can be used to speed up the process if the FTP server has a lot of files.
